===============================================================================
Preliminary notes:
------------------
Mark "o": new feature
Mark "*": bug fixed.
Mark "!": change that can break compatibility with older version
===============================================================================

version 3.0.5
=========================
o update button color scheme a little.
o now enable to set id property to all blocks.
o add new tag(ibox).
* fix tail check bug for a long word.
* fix tenten vertical position.
* wrap rotate element with block element(to propagate background color to rotated element).
! rename className prefix from 'nehan' to 'nehan3'(for version compatibility).

version 3.0.4
=========================
o Nehan3.Reader.onReady supported.
o Nehan3.Reader.onWriteLastNext supported.
o Nehan3.Reader.onWriteFirstPrev supported.
o Nehan3.DocumentParser.getPercent added.
* fix IE vertical alphabet bug in transitional mode.

version 3.0.3
=========================
o update default button design(use google-buttons)
o enable padding property(but not used yet, because IE has trouble about it)
o add new config(Pagerize.pgconfig.pager.nextLinkTextVert etc)

version 3.0.2, 2012/05/26
=========================
* fix logical param name(margin-before -> margin-start etc).
* disable kerning when base font size is too small.

version 3.0.1, 2012/05/22
==========================
o add config.system.conv_br

version 3.0.0, 2012/05/21
==========================
o first release